Steps to deploy the application into production:

1. Create an EC2 instance in AWS with any OS supported(using Amazon Linux 2 here)
2. Create the proper directory for the project along with config folder and docker-compose-prod.yml file.
3. Install docker
4. Install docker-compose from the resources bookmarked
5. Install git
6. Clone the git repo into the main directory, a Criador named repo will appear.
7. Create a new token and enter it while pushing some code.
8. Run the docker compose
9. Reinstall the express handler